{"tid":2204174,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【一場騙局】13歲偷嚐禁果成英國最年輕爸爸　5年後自爆親子鑑定發現戴綠帽","createTime":"2020-09-16T00:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T01:04:23.000Z","uid":293494,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e769861bd654e37a20e410e29c6ac027b9fdf5e0","tid":2204174,"uid":293494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"//原來，這一切都是策劃好的佈局，Chantelle父母的朋友跟英國媒體爆料，他們早就知道自己女兒跟很多人發生過性行為，但在女兒懷孕又不確定生父是誰的情況下，他們選定了年紀最輕的Alfie，因為如果對象是13歲的Alfie一定轟動全球的大新聞，果然如他們所料，這個故事在轉賣給媒體之後Chantelle的父母果真的賺到了一筆錢。而Alfie在發現小孩不是自己的之後想找Chantelle問清楚，卻發現他們全家帶著剛出生的女嬰消失了。//<br />\n<br />\n一切都係為左錢。。。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mamidaily.com/article/98168/%E4%B8%80%E5%A0%B4%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80-13%E6%AD%B2%E5%81%B7%E5%9A%90%E7%A6%81%E6%9E%9C%E6%88%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E3%80%805%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90%E9%91%91%E5%AE%9A%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E6%88%B4%E7%B6%A0%E5%B8%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmamidaily.com%2Farticle%2F98168%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%25A8%2599%25E5%25B1%2580-13%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2581%25B7%25E5%259A%2590%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%259E%259C%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E7%2588%25B8%25E7%2588%25B8%25E3%2580%25805%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%2591%2591%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%2588%25B4%25E7%25B6%25A0%25E5%25B8%25BD&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=9133242d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mamidaily.com/article/98168/%E4%B8%80%E5%A0%B4%E9%A8%99%E5%B1%80-13%E6%AD%B2%E5%81%B7%E5%9A%90%E7%A6%81%E6%9E%9C%E6%88%90%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%80%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E3%80%805%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90%E9%91%91%E5%AE%9A%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E6%88%B4%E7%B6%A0%E5%B8%BD</a>"},{"pid":"96d2a65473b5b3fa8f68fbdc672a